==Esperanto==
===Etymology===
Esperanto ''[[ĉi-]]'' (universal [[:Category:Esperanto correlatives|correlative]] prefix) + ''[[-u]]'' (correlative suffix of individuals)

===Correlative===
'''ĉiu''' (''plural'' '''[[ĉiuj]]''', ''accusative singular'' '''[[ĉiun]]''', ''accusative plural'' '''[[ĉiujn]]''')

# each one, [[everyone]], each person. (The universal correlative of individuals.)

